This paper is likely to belong to the category of Computer Science - Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) as it deals with the detection of Denial of Service (DOS) attacks, which is a major security concern in network security. 

It could also belong to the category of Computer Science - Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) as it deals with network traffic analysis and anomaly detection. 

The paper also uses machine learning classifiers, which could place it in the category of Computer Science - Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) or Computer Science - Machine Learning (cs.LG). 

Finally, the paper deals with data security and completeness, which could place it in the category of Computer Science - Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
